{"tid":1530714,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（冇圖）靚女女學生帶黑色口罩，無聲抗議政府及黑警","createTime":"2019-09-02T04:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T13:19:55.000Z","uid":113326,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"54db34530aa5fdfb2ea4c629ec3e94e9ff6ea705","tid":1530714,"uid":113326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:39:24.000Z","msg":"個心地靚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係冇圖，但我想講佢型到仆街<br />\n<br />\n希望各位學生罷唔到課，都帶番個黑色口罩聲援下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a795e6128433f9dd561db086e40a67c6ecf5218b","tid":1530714,"uid":8290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"和理非，好無力，好忟？<br />\n要抗爭，只有十月一前每日堅持做以下既事，係堅持，堅唔到都要堅，係呢到發誓你堅持呢個九月，就一個月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 罷消費（任何福建幫、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、藍紅食店）好難？勇武難唔難？<br />\n2. 低享樂（要發洩，做運動、十點9叫、唔好taobao消費食好野）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 每日like and share 1個文宣post<br />\n5. 下載Twitter 開acc,每日出1個post<br />\n6. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣教育自由行。<br />\n7. 每星期去連儂貼3張文宣<br />\n8. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n9. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n10. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n11. Tag或吹你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n<br />\n諗到再加，如果你咁都做唔到，講咩野好忟好惱無野可做。<br />\n只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"6eec4b9188ce9927eb3a1e2adeecbd2f622c8a22","tid":1530714,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"係咪話我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2cb15e6428024864f7f0deec69474833681f73","tid":1530714,"uid":113326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6eec4b9188ce9927eb3a1e2adeecbd2f622c8a22","tid":1530714,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"係咪話我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:19:55.